messages.content:
I identified all U.S. universities ranked in the CSRankings AI area (excluding Information Retrieval) for 2019–2024 and within 500 driving miles of the Natural History Museum of Los Angeles County. I then computed shortest driving distances and saved the results sorted by distance (and by higher rank on ties).

The file has been saved as:
- /workspace/dumps/workspace/AI_univ_LA_500miles_Top30_2024.json
